our shadow corp isn&#039;t running, that&#039;s another random person out there generating coin and raising the bar for the coin generator.<br /><br />So by the time it&#039;s all said and done, you would be going back to that person to ask for another 1 million since the network got harder while you were getting setup.<br /><br />People and Corporations try to &quot;buy&quot; the lottery all the time. Sometimes it works, but more times it fails because you just can&#039;t buy luck.<br /><br />Maybe if that person had started with 1.5 million when this project first started, but now I think it&#039;s beyond a feasible and logistics point to game the system. It&#039;s like trying to shut down the Pirate Bay now&nbsp; ;)</div>
